# UI stack (RSC + Tailwind)

## Structure

- Pages: Server Components in `src/app/pages/`
- Interactive forms / state: small `"use client"` files under `src/app/components/` (see `hello-form.tsx`)
- Document shell: `src/app/document.tsx` — stylesheet via `?url` for RSC HTML
- Optional providers: `src/app/providers.tsx` — add your design-system theme here
- Styles: `src/app/styles.css` (Tailwind), linked from `Document` via `?url`

## Styling

- **Tailwind** for layout, spacing, and page chrome
- Add a design system via `providers.tsx` and component imports when ready
- Prefer utility classes over raw hex/px for prototypes

## Patterns

- Server page + client form: `src/app/pages/home.tsx` + `src/app/components/hello-form.tsx`
- Presentational + interactive card: `src/app/components/info-card.tsx`

## Routes

Register new pages in `src/worker.tsx` with `route()` like the home page.
